    .HorizontalGrid-cell
      .GridCell
        .GridCell-content
          h3.Heading.Heading--small.u-smallMargin
            | Design is a method of solving problems.
          p.Text
            ' Design isn’t just about making things look good.
            | We want to design the user’s experience, and make products that are tailored to perfection.

  .HorizontalGrid.HorizontalGrid--limited.u-largeMargin
    .HorizontalGrid-cell
      .GridCell
        .GridCell-content
          .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--right
            h3.Heading.Heading--small.u-smallMargin
              | Restlessly pursue excellence.
            p.Text
              ' We believe the old adage that says good is the enemy of great.
              | We will not stop until all the work we do has reached its full potencial.
    .HorizontalGrid-cell
